    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary, showroom-ready condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every detail, from the flawless exterior luster to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a history of meticulous stewardship and climate-controlled storage. Mechanically indistinguishable from its original production state, it offers a driving experience that is both refined and uncompromising. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire an investment-grade example of unrivaled quality.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
