      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and optimized double-VANOS timing. This specimen is mated to a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock for superior power delivery. The chassis is exceptionally rigid, having undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive rod bearing service to ensure mechanical longevity. Suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with zero bushing deflection, offering the precise, communicative feedback synonymous with this platform. Finished in an immaculate factory coat with a pristine interior, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity to own a mechanically synchronized and aesthetically flawless icon of Bavarian engineering.",
